<%= header(1, 'What is this') %>
<p class="section">
  This is a simulator rolling the rare gacha (rare cat capsule) for
  Battle Cats. With the simulator, you can look into the future to
  predict your future rolling results.
</p>

<%= header(1, 'How to use') %>
<p class="section">
  First, you'll want to find your current seed.
</p>

<%= header(2, 'Seek the seed') %>
<ol>
  <li>Pick a gacha event (e.g. <em>Ultra Souls</em> or <em>Uberfest</em>)</li>
  <li>Use your rare (gold) tickets or cat food</li>
  <li>Roll several times. Preferably 7 to 10 rolls. Record the results</li>
  <li>The more rolls you made, the more accurate the result will be</li>
  <li><em>Don't</em> fill in any <a href="#what-is-a-guaranteed-roll">guaranteed rolls</a></li>
  <li>Fill the results in <a href="<%= seek_uri %>">seed seeking</a>. Make sure you pick the gacha event you rolled</li>
  <li>If everything is correct, you'll get the <strong>seed number</strong>, and two links</li>
  <li>One link is for debugging purpose, showing the status <em>before</em> you rolled</li>
  <li>The other link will show you the current status, <em>after</em> you rolled</li>
  <li>If you have other cats rolled without filling in the form, count yourself
  <li>Note that a <a href="#what-is-a-guaranteed-roll">guaranteed roll</a> counts as a half roll and thus will switch your track</a></li>
</ol>

